column2: SELECT TOP #   m.OBJID AS AKARI_ID,   m.RA AS AKARI_RA,   m.DEC AS AKARI_DEC,      n.objid AS SDSS_ID,      o.z AS zsp,   o.zErr AS e_zsp,	   o.zWarning AS zWarning,    o.class AS class,   o.subClass AS subclass,      n.distance AS SEPARATION_AKARI_SDSS1#       into mydb.test_zsp_# from MyDB.akari AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.fluxObjID         where m.OBJID < #
